Metadata: The URL provided by Oregon Sea Grant no longer goes to the site for this online publication.

This bibliography of publications on seafood waste disposal has sections on composting, hydrolyzed fish/fish fertilizer, and waste management. Sea Grant will not be distributing hard copies. Instead, the publication is available at the web site address http://www-​seafood.ucdavis​.edu/Pubs/compo​st.htm.
